    dc:description "FIGURES 130 – 131. Hecatrishula atherae (Ansari, 1957 b) n. comb. ex Corvus corax laurencei: 130, male habitus, dorsal and ventral views. 131, female habitus, dorsal and ventral views." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/883230/files/figure.png" ;
